<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//APACHE//DTD Documentation V2.0//EN" "document-v20.dtd">
<document>
    <header>
        <title>Installing and using the Divvun tools on Windows 7</title>
    </header>
    <body>
        <section>
            <title>Getting the Divvun tools</title>
            <p><a href="http://divvun.no/static_files/MSOfficeDivvunTools.exe">
                Download http://www.divvun.no/static_files/DivvunInstaller.exe</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <title>Installing the Divvun tools on Windows 7</title>

             <warning>If you upgrade from version 1, you must uninstall the old version before installing Divvun version 2.x.
                 </warning>
            <ol>
                <li>Click on the download link. The installer will start automatically. </li>

                <li>Choose which language you would like to use while installing the program:
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/installerer_velg_sprak-win7-nob.png"
                        alt="Choose installer language"/>
                    </p>
                </li>

                <li>Click Accept in the <strong>License agreement</strong>-window
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/installerer_lisens-win7-nob.png"
                        alt="Accept the license"/>
                    </p>
                </li>

                <li>To install the program, click the <strong>Install</strong> button.
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/installerer_installer-win7-nob.png"
                        alt="Click the &quot;Install&quot; button"/>
                    </p>
                </li>

                <li>The program is now installed.
                    Click the <strong>Close</strong> button to close the last dialog window:
                    <p>
                        <img src="images/installerer_lukk-win7-nob.png"
                        alt="Quit installer"/>
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </body>
</document>
